    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="5678f-102">강력한 클라이언트 및 서비스 [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] 프로그램에서 통신 중 throw될 수 있는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 개체를 처리합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-102">Robust client and service [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/includes/indigo1-md.md)] applications handle <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> objects that may be thrown during communication.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5678f-103">클라이언트에서도 자주 예상하는 두 개의 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 파생 예외 형식(<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> 및 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>)이 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-103">There are also two <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived exception types (<xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> and <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException>) that clients also often expect.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5678f-104">제네릭 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 처리기에서 이처럼 좀 더 구체적인 예외 형식을 catch하지 않도록 하려면 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>을 처리하기 전에 이러한 예외를 catch합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-104">Therefore, in order to prevent the generic <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> handler from catching these more specific exception types, catch these exceptions prior to handling <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="5678f-105">양방향 작업(즉, <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601>가 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute>로 설정된 <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> 특성이 있는 메서드)에 대한 응답으로 작업 계약에서 지정한 SOAP 오류를 받은 경우 클라이언트에서 `false` 개체가 throw됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-105"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException%601> objects are thrown on the client when a SOAP fault that is specified in the operation contract is received in response to a two-way operation (that is, a method with an <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute> attribute with <xref:System.ServiceModel.OperationContractAttribute.IsOneWay%2A> set to `false`).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5678f-106">수신기에서 작업 계약에 예상되거나 지정되지 않은 SOAP 오류를 받은 경우 <xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> 개체가 throw됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-106"><xref:System.ServiceModel.FaultException> objects are thrown when a listener receives a SOAP fault that is not expected or specified in the operation contract.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5678f-107">이러한 상황은 응용 프로그램이 디버깅 중이고 서비스에서 <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> 속성을 `true`로 설정한 경우에 주로 발생합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-107">This usually occurs when the application is being debugged and the service has the <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceBehaviorAttribute.IncludeExceptionDetailInFaults%2A> property set to `true`.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="5678f-108">사용자 지정 채널 및 바인딩 요소를 구현하는 경우 구성 요소에서 <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> 또는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 파생 개체만 throw하는 것이 좋습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-108">When implementing custom channels and binding elements, it is strongly recommended that your components throw only <xref:System.TimeoutException?displayProperty=nameWithType> or <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException>-derived objects.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="5678f-109">해당 구성 요소에 대해서만 복구할 수 있는 예외를 throw할 경우 해당 예외를 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 개체 내에서 래핑합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-109">In the case where your components throw a recoverable exception that is specific to the component, wrap that exception inside a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> object.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="5678f-110">디자인 및 WCF 오류 시스템을 사용 하는 방법에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 하십시오. [지정 및 계약 및 서비스에서 처리 오류](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-110">For more details about designing and using the WCF fault system, see [Specifying and Handling Faults in Contracts and Services](~/docs/framework/wcf/specifying-and-handling-faults-in-contracts-and-services.md).</span></span>  
  
> [!IMPORTANT]
>  <span data-ttu-id="5678f-111">WCF 런타임 throw 하지 것입니다는 <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> 있는 WCF 런타임 유지 하 고 사용자 코드가 실행 지점에서 처리 하는 안전 하지 않습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="5678f-111">The WCF Runtime will not throw a <xref:System.ServiceModel.CommunicationException> that is unsafe to handle at the point where it leaves the WCF Runtime and enters user code.</span></span>  
  
   
  
